[angry trumpeting]

189
00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:35.680
An elephant hair?

190
00:15:35.760 --> 00:15:38.440
Like I said,
it's stupid, right?

191
00:15:38.520 --> 00:15:41.240
Listen, take it from me.
Go home. Okay?

192
00:15:41.320 --> 00:15:43.440
Who needs this aggravation?

193
00:15:43.520 --> 00:15:46.120
You know, I'm probably
gonna leave soon myself.

194
00:15:46.200 --> 00:15:49.160
You go, I'll catch up,
all right?

195
00:15:49.200 --> 00:15:52.400
You see? Leave it to me.
I told you I could...

196
00:15:52.480 --> 00:15:54.920
- Tarzan! Tarzan!
- [Tarzan shouting]

197
00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:56.680
No!

198
00:16:03.200 --> 00:16:04.600
