in seconds?

252
00:19:07.720 --> 00:19:11.040
What? He's not a piranha!
He's...

253
00:19:11.080 --> 00:19:13.280
- [coughing]
- [Terk] He's alive!

254
00:19:13.360 --> 00:19:15.600
He's alive! He's alive!

255
00:19:15.680 --> 00:19:17.640
- He's alive!
- He's...

256
00:19:17.760 --> 00:19:19.080
You idiot!

257
00:19:19.160 --> 00:19:22.080
You nearly gave me a
heart attack! You happy?

258
00:19:22.120 --> 00:19:23.160
Uh-huh.

259
00:19:23.240 --> 00:19:24.560
You...

260
00:19:24.680 --> 00:19:26.920
I don't believe it.
You got the hair?

261
00:19:27.000 --> 00:19:31.760
Is that what
this is all about?
I got a whole tail of them.

262
00:19:31.800 --> 00:19:33.720
- [Kala] Tarzan?
- [ape mother] Terkina?

263
00:19:33.760 --> 00:19:35.240
[Terk] Oh, no.

264
00:19:35.360 --> 00:19:37.920
- Who's that?
- [both] My mom.

265
00:19:37.960 --> 00:19:39.600
- [Kala] Tarzan.
- Hi.

266
00:19:39.640 --> 00:19:42.040
- Hi, Aunt Kala.
- Oh, you scared me!

267
00:19:42.080 --> 00:19:44.320
- What happened?
- Well, I...

268
00:19:44.400 --> 00:19:46.440
Um, it's sort of a long...
It's involved.

269
00:19:46.480 --> 00:19:48.680
Because what happened,
it was a weird...

270
00:19:48.760 --> 00:19:50.720
What happened?

271
00:19:53.080 --> 00:19:56.320
- It was my fault, Kerchak.
- Tarzan.

272
00:19:56.400 --> 00:20:01.160
We were playing, and...
Well, I'm sorry, Kerchak.

273
00:20:01.240 --> 00:20:03.280
You almost killed someone.

274
00:20:03.360 --> 00:20:05.520
- It was an accident.
- He's only a child.

275
00:20:05.600 --> 00:20:08.080
That's no excuse.
You can't keep defending him.

276
00:20:08.120 --> 00:20:09.200
But he'll learn.

277
00:20:09.280 --> 00:20:11.120
He will not. You can't
learn to be one of us.

278
00:20:11.200 --> 00:20:14.000
- You never give him a chance.
- Give him a chance?

279
00:20:14.080 --> 00:20:18.120
[Kerchak] Kala, look at him.
He will never be one of us.

280
00:20:18.200 --> 00:20:20.080
[Kala] Kerchak!

281
00:20:20.640 --> 00:20:22.480
Tarzan.

282
00:20:23.080 --> 00:20:24.960
[sighs]

283
00:20:48.400 --> 00:20:51.920
[panting, shouting]

284
00:21:04.520 --> 00:21:07.120
[grunting]

285
00:21:13.040 --> 00:21:15.640
Tarzan,
what are you doing?

286
00:21:16.200 --> 00:21:18.040
Why am I so different?

287
00:21:18.120 --> 00:21:20.280
Because you're covered
with mud, that's why.

288
00:21:20.360 --> 00:21:22.200
No! Kerchak said
I didn't belong in...

289
00:21:22.280 --> 00:21:23.480
[Kala] Close your mouth.

290
00:21:23.520 --> 00:21:25.840
Kerchak said I don't
belong in the family.

291
00:21:25.880 --> 00:21:28.360
Never mind what Kerchak said.

292
00:21:28.400 --> 00:21:31.320
- Hold still.
- But look at me!

293
00:21:33.560 --> 00:21:35.720
I am, Tarzan.

294
00:21:35.800 --> 00:21:37.520
And do you know what I see?

295
00:21:37.560 --> 00:21:41.000
I see two eyes, like mine,

296
00:21:41.040 --> 00:21:45.520
and a nose, somewhere. Ah!

297
00:21:45.560 --> 00:21:47.040
Here.

298
00:21:47.120 --> 00:21:49.840
Two ears.

299
00:21:49.880 --> 00:21:53.360
- And let's see, what else?
- Two hands?

300
00:21:53.400 --> 00:21:55.080
That's right. [laughs]

301
00:22:06.240 --> 00:22:08.120
[sighs]

302
00:22:11.400 --> 00:22:14.000
Close your eyes.

303
00:22:14.080 --> 00:22:16.480
Now, forget what you see.

304
00:22:16.560 --> 00:22:18.480
What do you feel?

305
00:22:19.760 --> 00:22:21.240
My heart.

306
00:22:21.280 --> 00:22:23.200
Come here.

307
00:22:24.760 --> 00:22:26.760
- Your heart.
- See?

308
00:22:26.800 --> 00:22:29.360
We're exactly the same.

309
00:22:31.920 --> 00:22:34.880
Kerchak just can't see that.

310
00:22:37.040 --> 00:22:38.960
I'll make him see it.

311
00:22:39.000 --> 00:22:41.840
I'll be the best ape ever.

312
00:22:41.920 --> 00:22:44.160
[chuckles] Oh, I bet you will.

