00:39:05.480 --> 00:39:09.200
[gasps] Oh! Um...

508
00:39:09.280 --> 00:39:12.280
- [heartbeat]
- Oh...

509
00:39:15.920 --> 00:39:17.160
Oh, dear.

510
00:39:17.240 --> 00:39:19.560
Oh, dear, oh, dear.
Oh, dear.

511
00:39:20.400 --> 00:39:21.480
Yes, thank you.

512
00:39:21.560 --> 00:39:25.480
That's a lovely heartbeat.
It's very nice.

513
00:39:27.600 --> 00:39:29.680
- It's very nice.
- Oh, thank you.

514
00:39:29.760 --> 00:39:33.240
I can't do a thing with it
in this humidity though.
It's...

515
00:39:33.280 --> 00:39:34.720
You do speak!

516
00:39:34.800 --> 00:39:36.240
All this time
I thought you were

517
00:39:36.280 --> 00:39:38.720
a big, wild, quiet,
silent person thing.

518
00:39:38.800 --> 00:39:40.120
Why didn't you tell me?

519
00:39:40.160 --> 00:39:42.960
I must say I'm rather curious
as to who you are. I'd love...

520
00:39:44.400 --> 00:39:46.880
[grunts] Tarzan.

521
00:39:50.960 --> 00:39:53.120
Tarzan.

522
00:39:54.080 --> 00:39:55.800
Tarzan?

523
00:39:55.880 --> 00:39:57.880
[grunting]

524
00:39:59.120 --> 00:40:00.880
Oh, I see.

525
00:40:01.000 --> 00:40:03.040
Oh, I see.

526
00:40:03.120 --> 00:40:04.800
Tarzan.

527
00:40:04.920 --> 00:40:06.920
Oh, I see.

528
00:40:07.000 --> 00:40:10.480
No, no, no. No.
[clears throat]

529
00:40:10.520 --> 00:40:12.640
I'm Jane.

530
00:40:12.720 --> 00:40:17.240
No, no, no. No.
I'm Jane.

531
00:40:17.320 --> 00:40:19.040
No, no.

532
00:40:19.120 --> 00:40:22.280
Jane. Tarzan.

533
00:40:22.320 --> 00:40:24.000
Jane.

534
00:40:24.680 --> 00:40:26.080
Jane.

535
00:40:27.120 --> 00:40:29.320
- Exactly.
- [gunshot]

536
00:40:29.360 --> 00:40:30.640
Clayton!

537
00:40:33.320 --> 00:40:35.400
- [gunshot]
- Clayton.

538
00:40:35.480 --> 00:40:38.080
Extraordinary.

539
00:40:38.160 --> 00:40:42.400
Please, can you
take me to my camp?

540
00:40:42.480 --> 00:40:46.240
- [gunshot]
- Yes, Clayton. Wonderful.

541
00:40:46.320 --> 00:40:50.880
[stammering]
Um, can't we walk?

542
00:40:50.960 --> 00:40:53.720
[Tarzan] Can't we walk?!

543
00:40:55.160 --> 00:40:58.320
[all] Tarzan! Tarzan!
Where are you?

544
00:40:58.360 --> 00:41:00.400
[ape] Let's hope we find him
before Kerchak.

545
00:41:00.480 --> 00:41:01.960
[ape 2] Maybe he's lost.

546
00:41:02.040 --> 00:41:04.040
[ape 1] Or found something
more interesting.

547
00:41:04.120 --> 00:41:07.360
[Terk] Are you nuts?
What could be more
interesting than us?

548
00:41:07.400 --> 00:41:10.560
Hey, what's everybody
looking at? [gasps]

549
00:41:10.600 --> 00:41:13.200
[Tantor gasping]

550
00:41:16.720 --> 00:41:17.960
The horror!

551
00:41:18.080 --> 00:41:19.880
[whimpering] It's gruesome.
Hide me!

552
00:41:19.920 --> 00:41:23.040
Pull yourself together.
You're embarrassing me.

553
00:41:23.080 --> 00:41:25.600
These things aren't alive.

554
00:41:25.680 --> 00:41:27.720
- [laughter]
- I knew that.

555
00:41:27.840 --> 00:41:30.960
[all] Tarzan!

556
00:41:31.040 --> 00:41:32.800
Hello?

557
00:41:34.320 --> 00:41:38.760
What kind of primitive beasts
are responsible for this mess?

558
00:41:40.000 --> 00:41:42.000
Oh!

559
00:41:46.600 --> 00:41:49.080
Wow! Come here, you guys!
Come here, come here!

560
00:41:49.120 --> 00:41:51.040
- Look at this.
- What is that thing?

561
00:41:51.080 --> 00:41:53.000
- Funny. Wow.
- [dings]

562
00:41:53.080 --> 00:41:55.200
[all] Oooh!

563
00:41:57.800 --> 00:42:00.640
- [shattering]
- [Terk] Hey!

564
00:42:00.720 --> 00:42:03.040
Do it again, do it again.

565
00:42:03.120 --> 00:42:04.600
Like this?

566
00:42:04.640 --> 00:42:07.120
- [tearing]
- [Terk] Yeah!

567
00:42:09.040 --> 00:42:10.800
Yeah. Rip it!

568
00:42:12.080 --> 00:42:14.360
Ding! I love that part.

569
00:42:15.680 --> 00:42:17.880
Let me hear it, big fella.

570
00:42:17.960 --> 00:42:20.640
- [Terk] Now, hit it!
- [laughter]

571
00:42:22.120 --> 00:42:24.120
Yeah!

572
00:42:26.640 --> 00:42:28.120
Nice.

573
00:42:29.120 --> 00:42:31.200
What the heck? Bye-bye.

574
00:42:31.280 --> 00:42:33.720
Terk. [trumpets]

575
00:42:33.800 --> 00:42:35.480
Yeah, Tant.

576
00:42:35.560 --> 00:42:37.800
Now, hit it.

577
00:42:37.840 --> 00:42:40.600
- Come on, Tantor.
- [trumpets]

578
00:42:40.640 --> 00:42:42.640
[Terk] I love it.

579
00:42:42.680 --> 00:42:44.120
Stay with me, fellas.

580
00:42:44.160 --> 00:42:47.440
I feel something
happening here.

581
00:42:47.480 --> 00:42:51.840
[animals play music
with items in camp]

582
00:42:51.880 --> 00:42:56.640
