Do-be-do-da-ba-da-ba-do ♪

583
00:42:56.720 --> 00:43:02.320
[gorillas]
♪ Shoo-bee-do-da-be-da
Do-be-do-da-ba-da-ba-do ♪

584
00:43:02.400 --> 00:43:06.600
[all] ♪ Shoo-bee-do-da-be-da
Do-be-do-da-ba-da-ba-do ♪

585
00:43:06.680 --> 00:43:11.480
