736
00:52:07.640 --> 00:52:12.680
♪ Come with me now
to see my world ♪

737
00:52:12.720 --> 00:52:16.720
♪ Where there's beauty
beyond your dreams ♪

738
00:52:16.800 --> 00:52:20.800
♪ Can you feel
the things I feel ♪

739
00:52:20.880 --> 00:52:25.040
♪ Right now, with you ♪

740
00:52:26.760 --> 00:52:29.040
♪ Take my hand ♪

741
00:52:29.080 --> 00:52:33.560
♪ There's a world
I need to know ♪

742
00:52:50.720 --> 00:52:53.360
[Clayton] We've wasted all
this time on what he wants.

743
00:52:53.440 --> 00:52:57.480
The boat could arrive any day.
Now, ask him straight out.

744
00:53:00.520 --> 00:53:04.400
Tarzan, will you take us
