746
00:53:06.600 --> 00:53:08.760
I understand.

747
00:53:08.800 --> 00:53:10.760
- Good work, Jane.
- Well?

748
00:53:10.840 --> 00:53:13.280
- I can't.
- What?

749
00:53:13.320 --> 00:53:16.560
- Why not, Tarzan?
- Kerchak.

